metadata.name: OurDegenLife
metadata.description: By owning this NFT, you will get royalties every week number 4, as long as there hasn't been a different owner within the last 7 days prior to the pay out of that week (day might fluctuate due to Market Places delay). This NFT is Tier 4. Tier 4 NFTs are entitled to receive, on a weekly Tier basis, 18% of the total royalties to be split amongst a maximum of 75 NFTs (if no owner change last 7 days)
